<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Ticket Status Updated</title>
<style>
body {
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  background:#f4f6f8;
  padding:20px;
}
.container {
  max-width:600px;
  margin:auto;
  background:#ffffff;
  border-radius:8px;
  padding:25px;
  box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}
.header {
  background:#16a34a;
  color:white;
  padding:15px;
  border-radius:6px;
  text-align:center;
  font-size:20px;
  font-weight:bold;
}
.content {
  margin-top:20px;
  color:#333;
}
.ticket-box {
  background:#ecfdf5;
  padding:15px;
  border-radius:6px;
  margin-top:15px;
}
.label {
  font-weight:bold;
}
.status {
  font-weight:bold;
  color:#16a34a;
}
.footer {
  margin-top:25px;
  font-size:12px;
  text-align:center;
  color:#777;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="container">

<div class="header">
📢 Ticket Status Updated
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>Your support ticket has been updated.</p>

<div class="ticket-box">
<p><span class="label">Ticket Number:</span> {{ticketNumber}}</p>
<p><span class="label">Title:</span> {{title}}</p>
<p><span class="label">Status:</span> <span class="status">{{status}}</span></p>
<p><span class="label">Remarks:</span> {{remarks}}</p>
</div>

<p>If you have any questions, please contact support.</p>
</div>

<div class="footer">
© {{currentYear}} Ticket System
</div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
